In re Kavanagh’s Estate. In re Sisters of the Poor. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 14, 1890.)

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

No opinion. No appeal having been taken to the court of appeals, this motion for a stay denied. See 5 N. Y. Supp. 676, 6 N. Y. Supp. 669, and ante, 443.
